That's the lowest price we could find by $10. It includes eight hardcover books that can be read aloud by the Me Reader. Three AAA batteries are required (included). Deal ends January 6.

title: Prepworks by Progressive 6pc ProKeeper Set
description: Amazon offers the Prepworks by Progressive 6-Piece ProKeeper Set for $35.99 with free shipping. That's the lowest price we could find by $24. It includes a 4-quart, 2.5-quart, 1.5-quart, 1.4-quart, and two 1.5-cup containers with air-tight silicone seals.

title: Jegs Performance 3-Drawer Tool Box
description: Jegs via eBay offers its Jegs Performance 3-Drawer Tool Box for $30.97 with free shipping. That's $5 under our December mention, $19 off, and the lowest price we've seen. Features include a central lock, carrying handle, and two latches.

title: T-fal Performa 3qt Stainless Steel Sauce Pan
description:
Amazon offers the T-fal Performa 3-Quart Stainless Steel Sauce Pan for $12.74 with free shipping for Prime members. (Target charges the same with in-store pickup.) That's $17 off and the lowest price we could find. It's dishwasher-safe and oven safe to 500 degrees.

Update: It's now out of stock at Amazon; however, Target still offers it for $12.74 with in-store pickup.

title: Nike Men's Dunk High Basketball Shoes
description: Nike offers its Nike Men's Dunk High Basketball Shoes in White/Red or White/Black for $69.97. In cart, that drops to $52.48. Plus, Nike+ members receive free shipping. (Not a member? It's free to join.) That's $48 off list and the lowest price we could find. They're available in select sizes from 7 to 15. Deal ends January 4.

title: Intex Mossy Oak Twin Downy Air Mattress
description: Walmart offers the Intex Mossy Oak Twin Prestige Downy Airbed Mattress for $15.97. Opt for in-store pickup to avoid the $49.97 shipping fee. That's $14 off list and the lowest price we could find, although we saw it for $4 less in September. It features a flocked top and 3-in-1 valve with extra-wide openings.

title: WowWee Sesame Street Elmoji Coding Robot
description: Amazon offers the WowWee Sesame Street Elmoji Junior Coding Robot in Red for $17.38 $16.96 with free shipping for Prime members. That's $2 under last week's mention, $43 off list, and the lowest price we've seen. It develops STEM skills using an emoji-based coding language and can be used in conjunction with the Elmoji iOS or Android app.

title: Crew Furniture Urban Child Recliner
description: Jet.com offers the Crew Furniture Urban Child Recliner in Moonbeam for $49 with free shipping. That's tied with our mention from last week and the lowest price we could find by $26. It features a push-back reclining mechanism and microsuede upholstery.

title: Dell Celeron 1.6GHz 12" Touch Chromebook
description: Dell Small Business offers its 2.8-lb. Dell Chromebook 11 3180 Intel Celeron Braswell 1.6GHz 11.6" Touchscreen Laptop in Black for $199 with free shipping. That's tied with our Cyber Monday mention and the lowest price we could find now by $90. It features an Intel Celeron N3060 1.6GHz Braswell dual-core processor, 11.6" 1366x768 (720p) touchscreen LCD, 4GB RAM, 16GB eMMC storage, USB 3.1, HDMI, 3-cell battery, and Chrome OS.

title: Toys"R"Us New Year's Sale
description:
Toys "R" Us takes 20% off select items via coupon code "NEWYEARS20" during its New Year's Sale. (Eligible items are marked.) Choose in-store pickup to avoid the $5.99 shipping fee, or spend $29 or more to bag free shipping. Deal ends January 6.

See all Toys"R"Us Coupons.

title: adidas Men's 350 Shoes
description: adidas via eBay offers the adidas Men's 350 Shoes in White for $40 with free shipping. That's $40 off and the lowest price we could find. They're available in sizes 8 to 12.

title: P90X Recovery Stick Self Massage Tool
description: Walmart offers the P90X Recovery Stick Self Massage Tool for $7.14. Opt for in-store pickup to dodge the $5.99 shipping fee. That's the lowest price we could find by $8. It features three independent massage rollers.

title: Reebok Men's Athletic Performance Jacket
description: Proozy offers the Reebok Men's Athletic Performance Jacket in several colors (Red pictured) for $14.99 with free shipping. That's tied with our Cyber Monday mention, $45 off, and the lowest price we've seen. It comes in select sizes from S to 5XL.

title: Yamaha Bluetooth Soundbar w/ Subwoofer
description: Newegg offers the Yamaha Bluetooth Sound Bar and Wireless Subwoofer for $154.95 with free shipping. That's tied with our Black Friday week mention and the lowest price we could find by $125. It features two 2-1/8" cone speakers, 6.5" subwoofer, 200-watt total output, and Bluetooth streaming.

title: Withings Unisex Activite Pop Fitness Watch
description: Walgreens offers the Withings Unisex Activite Pop Fitness Watch in Azure or Grey for $53.99. Coupon code "EXTRA18" cuts that to $44.27. With free shipping, that's $16 below our July mention and the lowest price we've seen. (It's the best deal now by $6.) It features a stainless steel case, silicone sport strap, HealthMate app for Android and iOS, and water resistance to 150 feet. Deal ends January 6.

title: TP-Link Archer AC3200 802.11ac WiFi Router
description: TigerDirect Business offers the TP-Link Archer AC3200 Tri-Band 802.11ac Wireless Gigabit Ethernet Router for $109.99 plus $2.99 for shipping. That's $7 under our October mention and the lowest price we could find now by $67. The tri-band wireless router (2.4GHz and two 5GHz) features a 1GHz dual-core processor, four Gigabit Ethernet ports, USB 3.0, and six antennas.

title: Roccat Kave XTD Headset w/ Syva Headphones
description:
Dell Home offers the Roccat Kave XTD Stereo Gaming Headset in Black bundled with the Roccat Syva In-Ear Headphones in Black/Blue for $39.99 with free shipping. That's tied with last month's mention and the lowest price we could find for these items purchased separately elsewhere by $63.

The headset features 50mm neodymium drivers, a 20Hz to 20kHz frequency response, detachable and 360°-rotatable noise-canceling boom microphone, in-line remote, and 8-foot cable. The headphones feature 10mm drivers, a 20Hz to 20kHz frequency response, and in-line remote and microphone.

title: SwissGear Apastron 16" Laptop Backpack
description: Dell Small Business offers the SwissGear Apastron 16" Laptop Backpack in Navy Denim for $24.99 with free shipping. That's tied with our mention from two weeks ago and the lowest price we could find today by $35. It features a side-entry TripleProtect padded compartment that accommodates laptops up to 16", 10" tablet pocket, file divider, multiple exterior pockets, and adjustable shoulder straps.

title: Baz: Star Crossed Love Ticket in Las Vegas
description: Travelzoo offers an Adult Ticket to Baz Luhrmann's Baz: Star Crossed Love at The Palazzo in Las Vegas, NV, bundled with a glass of prosecco, with prices starting from $46.54 via coupon code "BZTZOOP". That's a savings of $18 and the lowest price we could find. Additional taxes and fees apply. Book this travel deal by January 31 for shows through March 31, 2018.

title: Gold's Gym Trainer 430i Treadmill w/ HRM
description: Walmart offers the Gold's Gym Trainer 430i Treadmill with Heart Rate Monitor for $339 with free shipping. That's $20 under our mention from the week of Black Friday, the best price we've seen, and a low now by $60. It features an LCD display, 16" x 50" tread belt, iFit technology, power incline, and a dual-grip heart rate monitor.

title: Lumsing 48W 4-Port USB Car Charger
description: Yangdock E-commerce via Amazon offers the Lumsing Quick Charge 2.0 48-watt 4-Port USB Car Charger in Black or White for $7.99. Coupon code "DA656129" cuts it to $5.99. Plus, Prime members bag free shipping. That's the lowest price we could find now by a buck. It features Quick Charge 2.0, which provides up to eight hours of battery life from 15 minutes of charging. Deal ends January 14.

title: Amazon First Reads eBook Program
description:
Amazon offers its Prime members one early-release Kindle eBook per month for free as part of its Amazon First Reads Program. (It costs $1.99 for non-members who sign up for Amazon First Reads monthly emails.) That's $5 under the list prices of these books, which are otherwise only available as preorders. Deal ends January 31.

Each month, you can choose from one of six new Kindle eBooks that are selected by Amazon's editors in advance of the books' official release dates. This month's titles include Renee Shafransky's Tips for Living, Cheryl Reid's As Good as True, and Scott J. Holliday's Punishment .

title: Ironman Essex 990 Inversion Table
description: Walmart offers the Ironman Essex 990 Inversion Table in Gray for $88 with free shipping. That's the lowest price we could find by $16. It inverts to a full 180° and helps relieve back pain and stress and keeps back muscles flexible. Features include a powder-coated 1.5" steel frame, 3/4" foam backrest, angle and height adjustability, pin-release ankle holder system, and 275-lb. weight capacity.

title: Exerpeutic Aero Air Elliptical
description: Walmart offers the Exerpeutic 260 Aero Air Elliptical for $78 with free shipping. (Amazon charges the same.) That's $2 under our October mention and the lowest price we've seen. (It's the best deal now by $9.) It features an LCD display, tension adjustment, and 260-lb. weight capacity.

title: Clarks Winter Clearance
description:
Clarks takes up to 50% off a selection of men's, women's, and kids' shoes as part of its Winter Clearance. (Prices are as marked.) Even better, cut an extra 20% off via coupon code "EXTRA20". Plus, all orders receive free shipping. That beats our mention from last week, which lacked the extra 20% off coupon. Deal ends January 10.

See all Clarks Coupons.

description:

  • Longines Women's Primaluna Stainless Steel Watch for $670 (low by $18)

title: Dell Inspiron Celeron 1.6GHz Dual 12" Laptop
description:
Dell Home, via its Member Purchase Program, offers its Dell Inspiron 11 3000 Series Intel Celeron Braswell 1.6GHz 11.6" Laptop in Alpine White for $146.99 with free shipping. That's tied with our mention from two weeks ago and the lowest price we could find by $53. It features an Intel Celeron N3060 1.6GHz Braswell dual-core processor, 11.6" 1366x768 (720p) LED-backlit LCD, 2GB RAM, 32GB eMMC storage, 802.11n wireless, Bluetooth 4.2, 2-cell battery, and Windows 10 Home 64-bit.

Note: Dell pictures it in blue, but this deal is for a white model per the specs.

description:

description: Walkintofashion via eBay offers the Guess Women's Drama Square Sunglasses in Gold/Black or Rose Gold/White for $39.19 with free shipping. That's $59 off and the lowest price we could find. They feature 60mm lenses.

title: Carnival 7Nt Caribbean Cruise
description: Vacations to Go offers a Carnival Cruise 7-Night Caribbean Cruise for Two, with prices starting from $908. That's the lowest price we could find by $40. This roundtrip cruise aboard the Carnival Glory departs from Miami, FL, on January 27. Book this travel deal by January 26.

title: NordVPN 3-Year VPN Subscription
description: NordVPN offers its NordVPN 3-Year VPN Subscription for $99 ($2.75/month). That's tied with last week's mention, $331 off list, and the lowest price we could find. The service features AES 256-bit encryption, 2,533 worldwide servers in 56 different countries, a no-logs policy, and automatic kill switch. You can connect up to six devices simultaneously, and it's compatible with Windows, Mac, iOS, Android, and more.

title: Dell XPS Coffee Lake i5 6-Core PC w/ 2GB GPU
description:

With free shipping, that's $114 off list, $14 below our mention from last week, and the lowest price we've seen. Deal ends February 3. Features include:
  • Intel Core i5-8400 2.8GHz Coffee Lake 6-core processor
  • 8GB RAM
  • 1TB 7200 rpm hard drive
  • AMD Radeon RX 560 2GB graphics
  • Windows 10 Home 64-bit

title: LEGO Batman Movie Alarm Clock
description: Toys"R"Us offers the LEGO Batman Movie Alarm Clock in Batgirl or Joker for $10.48. Coupon code "NEWYEARS20" cuts that to $8.38. It measures 9" tall and requires two AAA batteries (included). Coupon ends January 6.

Deal ends January 14.

title: Best Phone Deals: Snag an Unlocked Nokia Plus Extras for $47!
description: Snag a cheap cell phone today and start your new year off right! Score a refurb Galaxy S5, or opt for a brand-new Nokia that'll remind you of the good ol' days. Check out these offers and more in our roundup of the week's best phone deals.

title: Magellan Outdoors Women's Winter Boots
description: Academy Sports and Outdoors offers the Magellan Outdoors Women's Winter Boots in several styles (Front Zip Pac pictured) for $19.99. Pad your order over $25 to bag free shipping, otherwise shipping adds $8.01. Excluding padding, that's a savings of $10 and the best deal we could find. They're available in select sizes from 6 to 10.

title: Citizen Men's and Women's Watches at Jomashop
description:
Jomashop takes up to 79% off a selection of Citizen men's and women's watches. Plus, coupon code "DNEWSFS" bags free shipping for all orders. Sale ends January 5. A couple of best bets:
  • Citizen Women's Mother of Pearl Swarovski Crystals Watch for $59.99 + $0 s&h via "CZX20" (low by $1; $79+ elsewhere)
  • Citizen Men's Navihawk A-T Eco-Drive Chronograph Watch for $358 + $0 s&h via "AD10" (pictured, low by $6; $421+ elsewhere)

title: 8 Things to Buy in January (and 3 Things to Wait On)
description: Ready or not, 2018 is here! That means we're done with the holiday sales and on to the post-holiday sales. While you won't find everything on sale in January, some items are real bargains this time of year — like gym memberships, bedding, and hotel stays.

title: Massdrop Sennheiser HD 58X Jubilee Headphones
description:
Massdrop offers the Massdrop x Sennheiser HD 58X Jubilee Headphones in Black for $149.99 with free shipping. That's $136 less than the best price we could find for the Sennheiser HD 600, a similar build. These special edition headphones feature a design inspired by the Sennheiser HD 580 Precision headphones, but with 150-ohm drivers. Deal ends January 27.

Note: They're not expected to ship until June 29.
